HEADWORD: Sideroscope
<hw>Sid"er*o*scope</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[Gr. <?/<?/<?/
iron + <ets>-scope</ets>.]</ety> <def>An instrument for detecting small
